{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Shopify Liquid code examples","slogan":"Build and customize themes faster with component based Liquid examples"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"9d1261d3-9e59-5017-8b25-7e507f905b98","html":"<ol>\n<li>Locate the section file which contains your theme's blog article listing, such as <code class=\"language-text\">blog-template.liquid</code>, and paste the code below into the file.</li>\n<li>The section settings in this example can be placed inside the sections' existing schema array, if it is already present. For example, it can be placed within the section setting named <code class=\"language-text\">Blog pages</code>. In this case, the code within the <code class=\"language-text\">{% schema %}</code> tags below can be added within the existing schema settings (including a comma to separate from other settings).</li>\n<li>By default, tags for all blogs will appear. This can be disabled on the <a href=\"https://help.shopify.com/en/themes/development/theme-editor\">theme editor</a>.</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"twig\"><pre class=\"language-twig\"><code class=\"language-twig\"><span class=\"token other\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>aside</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token ld\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{%-</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span></span> <span class=\"token property\">section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property\">settings</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property\">blog_show_tags</span> <span class=\"token rd\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">-%}</span></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token other\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  